# title,size,x y name,footnote




## add title

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip, total_bill,color=sex)) + geom_point()+ ggtitle("tip by sex")
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-29-1.png){width=672}
:::
:::

## add subtitle

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip, total_bill,color=sex)) + geom_point()+ ggtitle("tip by sex",subtitle = "Subtitle of the plot")
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-30-1.png){width=672}
