## add footnote

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
p=ggplot(tips, aes(tip, total_bill,color=sex)) + geom_point()+ ggtitle("tip by sex")+labs(caption = "this is footnote")
p
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](1-ggplot2_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-31-1.png){width=672}
